  "dct_description_sm": [
    "The New Jersey Tax Parcels - Cumberland County, 2005 dataset represents tax lot information for Cumberland County, New Jersey. The table is derived from the MOD-IV file maintained by the New Jersey Department of the Treasury. Each mapped tax parcel has its own record, which is updated as part of the regular tax assessment process. The complete statewide file is 1.6 GB in size. This MS-Access file contains individual tables for each city, borough and township in the county and several lookup tables."
  ],
